data.description: Attention Investors!! Discover an incredible opportunity in Warren, MI! This 4-bedroom, 2-bath home is perfectly situated with easy access to freeways and mere minutes from 696 and 94. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this property is ready for your personal touch and offers immense potential. Whether you're looking to renovate or to flip. Don't miss out on this chance schedule your showing today.
